Pojďme.

15
00:00:42,009 --> 00:00:42,840
Dobře.

16
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:43,840
<i>V roce 2008,

17
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:47,048
<i>když jsme se do sebe zamilovali

18
