99
00:05:54,588 --> 00:05:55,670
Hyun Bi.

100
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,838
Hm.

101
00:05:58,550 --> 00:05:59,709
My...

102
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:05,550
