126
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,509
<i>VÝLET DO GAPYEONGU S JAE HYUNEM!

127
00:07:39,509 --> 00:07:40,959
<i>Ale Jae Hyun...

128
00:07:42,050 --> 00:07:43,129
